---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const seo = {"title": "Waxing & Sugaring | D‑Essence Wellness", "description": "Efficient hair removal with skin‑conscious techniques.", "canonical": "/services/waxing", "type": "website", "ogImage": "/og-default" };
---

<BaseLayout {...seo}>

<section class="relative isolate paper">

<style is:global>
  :root{
    --paper:#F8F6F2; --ink:#141414; --muted:#5a5a5a; --rule:#E6E1D8;
  }
  .paper{ background:var(--paper); color:var(--ink); }
  .rule{ border-color:var(--rule); }
  .muted{ color:var(--muted); }
  .measure{ max-width: 64ch; }
  .dropcap:first-letter{ float:left; font-size:3.2rem; line-height:1; padding-right:.35rem; padding-top:.2rem; font-weight:600; }
  .ataglance{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:.75rem 1.25rem; font-size:.95rem; color:var(--muted); }
  .ataglance span::after{ content:"·"; margin-left:1.25rem; color:var(--muted); }
  .ataglance span:last-child::after{ content:""; margin:0; }
  .pullquote{ border-left:2px solid var(--ink); padding-left:.85rem; font-style:italic; color:#3b3b3b; margin: 1.25rem 0; }
  @media (max-width: 1023px){ .side-col{ display:none; } }
  details.faq summary{ list-style:none; }
  details.faq summary::-webkit-details-marker{ display:none; }
  .faq-toggle{ width:1.1rem; height:1.1rem; margin-right:.5rem; flex:0 0 auto; }
  details.faq[open] .plus{ display:none; }
  details.faq:not([open]) .minus{ display:none; }
  .icon-check{ width:1.1rem; height:1.1rem; flex:0 0 auto; margin-top:.15rem;}
  .timeline{ position:relative; }
  .timeline::before{ content:""; position:absolute; left:.9rem; top:.25rem; bottom:.25rem; width:2px; background:var(--rule); }
  .tl-step{ position:relative; padding-left:2.25rem; }
  .tl-badge{ position:absolute; left:0; top:.1rem; width:1.8rem; height:1.8rem; border-radius:999px; background:var(--ink); color:#fff; font-size:.9rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-weight:600; }
  .tl-title{ font-weight:600; }
</style>

  <!-- HERO (left‑aligned, no breadcrumb) -->
  <div class="px-6 pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <p class="text-xs tracking-wider uppercase muted">Service</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-[2.75rem] md:text-6xl leading-[1.05] font-semibold tracking-tight">Waxing & Sugaring</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[1.125rem] md:text-xl muted measure">Efficient hair removal with skin‑conscious techniques.</p>
      <div class="mt-6 h-px w-full border-t rule"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- BODY -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-24 grid grid-cols-12 gap-8">

    <!-- Removed left side labels entirely -->

    <!-- Main narrative -->
    <article class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 xl:col-span-7">
      <!-- DESCRIPTION (unique, professional) -->
      <section id="description" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Description</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 muted dropcap">Both methods are fast, hygienic, and suitable for most body areas. Your provider will choose the formula best suited to your skin sensitivity, hair type, and treatment area to maximize comfort and results. With consistent appointments, regrowth often becomes finer and sparser over time.</p>
        <p class="mt-3 muted">
          It works by temporarily blocking nerve signals to specific muscles, softening lines such as frown lines, forehead creases, and crow’s feet.
          Results develop within a few days and last around 3–4 months, leaving the skin smoother and the appearance refreshed while maintaining natural expressions.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-attributes mt-6 flex flex-nowrap whitespace-nowrap items-center gap-1.5 sm:gap-2 md:gap-3 overflow-x-auto md:overflow-visible pr-1" role="list"><li class="shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-2 rounded-full border rule bg-white px-2 py-1 md:px-3 md:py-1.5 text-[11px] md:text-sm font-medium text-neutral-800 shadow-sm"><span class="rounded-full bg-neutral-900 h-1 w-1 md:h-1.5 md:w-1.5"></span>Pure formula</li><li class="shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-2 rounded-full border rule bg-white px-2 py-1 md:px-3 md:py-1.5 text-[11px] md:text-sm font-medium text-neutral-800 shadow-sm"><span class="rounded-full bg-neutral-900 h-1 w-1 md:h-1.5 md:w-1.5"></span>3–4 months</li><li class="shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-2 rounded-full border rule bg-white px-2 py-1 md:px-3 md:py-1.5 text-[11px] md:text-sm font-medium text-neutral-800 shadow-sm"><span class="rounded-full bg-neutral-900 h-1 w-1 md:h-1.5 md:w-1.5"></span>Non‑surgical</li><li class="shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-2 rounded-full border rule bg-white px-2 py-1 md:px-3 md:py-1.5 text-[11px] md:text-sm font-medium text-neutral-800 shadow-sm"><span class="rounded-full bg-neutral-900 h-1 w-1 md:h-1.5 md:w-1.5"></span>Natural results</li></ul>
        <p class="pullquote">“Smoothed lines, natural movement.”</p>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- BENEFITS (unchanged from v2) -->
      <section id="benefits" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Benefits</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-10 gap-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 muted"><svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>Long‑lasting smoothness—typically 3–4 weeks between sessions.</div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 muted"><svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>Finer, lighter regrowth with consistent treatments.</div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 muted"><svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>Gentle options for sensitive skin (sugaring is water‑soluble and less adherent to live skin).</div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 muted"><svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>Natural exfoliation for a smoother look and feel.</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- THE PROCESS (unchanged from v2) -->
      <section id="process" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">The Process</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 timeline space-y-6">
          <div class="tl-step"><div class="tl-badge">1</div><p class="tl-title">Consultation</p><p class="muted mt-1">Assessment of goals and medical history, mapping injection points and confirming candidacy.</p></div>
          <div class="tl-step"><div class="tl-badge">2</div><p class="tl-title">Treatment</p><p class="muted mt-1">Small injections with a fine needle into targeted muscles; procedure usually takes 10–15 minutes.</p></div>
          <div class="tl-step"><div class="tl-badge">3</div><p class="tl-title">Follow‑Up</p><p class="muted mt-1">Results develop in 3–5 days with full effect at 2 weeks. Effects last about 3–4 months.</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- PRE / POST (unchanged from v2) -->
      <section id="care" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Pre and Post‑Treatment Instructions</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
          <div><p class="font-medium">Before your visit</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 muted mt-2 space-y-2"><li>Let hair grow to ~1/4 inch (6 mm) for best removal; avoid shaving for ~10–14 days pre‑visit.</li><li>Avoid tanning/self‑tanners for 48–72 hours before; use SPF if outdoors.</li><li>Pause retinoids, AHAs/BHAs, and harsh exfoliants on the area for ~3–5 days (longer if advised).</li><li>Gently exfoliate 24–48 hours before (not the same day). Arrive with clean, dry skin—no lotions, oils, or deodorant.</li></ul>
          </div>
          <div><p class="font-medium">After your visit</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 muted mt-2 space-y-2"><li>Expect mild redness or sensitivity for a few hours; apply cool compress or soothing gel if needed.</li><li>Avoid heat, tight clothing, workouts, pools, and saunas for 24–48 hours.</li><li>Skip exfoliants, retinoids, and fragranced products on the area for 2–3 days; moisturize gently.</li><li>Begin gentle exfoliation after 2–3 days to help prevent ingrowns; wear SPF and limit sun for 48–72 hours.</li></ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- FAQs (unchanged from v2) -->
      <section id="faqs" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer">Does it hurt?</summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">You may feel a quick sting during removal, which subsides immediately. Techniques like skin support, small sections, and soothing gel help keep you comfortable.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer">Waxing vs. Sugaring—what’s the difference?</summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Wax adheres to hair (and some to skin), removed opposite growth; sugaring is water‑soluble, applied against growth and removed with growth—often gentler with less breakage.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer">How long should my hair be?</summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">About 1/4 inch (6 mm) is ideal. If hair is very short, more passes may be required; if very long, trimming may be needed.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">Is the treatment painful?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Discomfort is minimal; injections feel like small pinches and are well tolerated.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">Are there side effects?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Side effects are usually mild and temporary, such as redness, swelling, or slight bruising at injection sites.</p></details>
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>

    <!-- Right margin notes (sticky cues) remain -->
    
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
